{
  "texts": [
    "The experiments necessitate the careful adjustment of several hyperparameters related to model training.",
    "The LSTM model in the TXtreme framework is composed of 4 layers followed by fully connected layers.",
    "Each LSTM layer is of size 100 LSTM cells and the last dense layer size equals the forecasting horizon for each dataset.",
    "The batch size for LSTM is 32 for all datasets and the learning rate is set to 0.001.",
    "As it is mentioned in section 4.3 loss function is set to Huber loss to counter the effect of any extreme values."
  ]
}